title: The Agent
description:
The redesigned Agent is the ultimate ditch and alley smasher. It features a unique shape with a wide platform and deep concave, functional kicktails, and cutouts that offer your feet points of reference for added control in carves and slides.

L: 35.00"
W: 9.50"
WB: 20.00"

Art by Eric Waetzig

Check out the Agent here: arborcollective.com/skate/boards/view/449679/agent
